Maratha Mandal Engineering College (MMEC) is located at R.S. No. 104, Halbhavi Village, New Vantmuri Post, Via-Kakati, Belagavi – 591113, Karnataka, India. Established in 1997, it is approved by AICTE and affiliated to VTU, Belagavi. Managed by Maratha Mandal (founded 1931). Website: https://www.mmec.edu.in. Contact: +91 9353364643, info@mmec.edu.in.
